overview.en: GT is a decentralized, global, secure, private, blockchain-based global green tea e-commerce system.The company is committed to making global consumption of green tea safe, private and easy for all consumers.
overview.zh: GT是一个去中心化的，全球性的，安全的，隐私的，基于区块链的全球绿茶电子商务系统。致力于让所有消费者，安全、隐私、轻易的进行全球性绿茶的消费。
